@{
    Layout = null;
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ganesh Sharma - Introduction</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #121212; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">

    <!-- Main container -->
    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: flex-start; min-height: 100vh; padding-top: 20px;">
        <div style="background: #1e1e1e; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); width: 50%; text-align: center;">

            <!-- Image Section -->
            <div style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
                <img src="~/images/gsversion2.jpg" alt="Ganesh Sharma" style="width: 150px; height: 150px; border-radius: 50%; border: 4px solid #4facfe; box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(79, 172, 254, 0.8);">
            </div>

            <!-- Name Section -->
            <h1 style="font-size: 2rem; color: #4facfe; margin-bottom: 10px; text-shadow: 0 0 15px #00f2fe;">
                Ganesh Sharma
            </h1>

            <!-- Sub-heading -->
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.2rem; color: #f39c12; margin-top: 0; text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(243, 156, 18, 0.8);">
                Software Engineer
            </h3>

            <!-- Description in Textarea -->
            <textarea readonly style="width: 100%; height: 300px; background-color: #1e1e1e; color: #ecf0f1; font-size: 1rem; border: 2px solid #4facfe; border-radius: 8px; padding: 10px; resize: none; overflow-y: auto;">
I hold a Master's Degree in Computer Application (MCA) and have over 5 years of experience in developing scalable and secure applications.
I specialize in building enterprise-level web applications using C#, Entity Framework Core, and SQL Server.
I am proficient in implementing REST APIs, Razor Pages, and integrating Razorpay for secure payment solutions.
I am also well-versed in using JavaScript, React, and Bootstrap to create dynamic and interactive UIs.
            </textarea>

            <!-- BACK TO MAIN PAGE Button -->
            <form asp-controller="FileUpload" asp-action="Index" method="get" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 20px;">
                <button type="submit" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, #4facfe, #00f2fe); border: none; padding: 12px 18px; border-radius: 8px; color: white; font-size: 16px; cursor: pointer; transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;">
                    BACK TO MAIN PAGE
                </button>
            </form>

        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
